### M4 — Second signal + confidence scoring
- **Provide:** Detection Signals section (Signal 2) + Uncertainty Representation + the Architecture diagram.
- **Ask it to generate:** The stylometry function (sentence-length variance + TTR → 0–1 score) and the scoring logic (`0.7·llm + 0.3·stylo` → threshold → attribution).
- **Verify:** Run clearly-AI and clearly-human texts and confirm scores vary meaningfully and land in the right buckets; confirm a mixed text lands in "uncertain" rather than flipping at 0.5.

### M5 — Production layer (labels, appeals, rate limiting, audit log)
